'''纽约州立大学水牛城分校法学院'''（SUNY Buffalo Law School）是一所自1887年起在[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[水牛城|水牛城]]创设的法学院，现附属于[[纽约州立大学水牛城分校|纽约州立大学水牛城分校]]。
该学院在《[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]》的[[美国法学院排名|法学院排名]]中排名86名。<ref name="Top 2012 Law School Rankings">{{cite web | url=http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/cuny-03106 | title=Top 2012 Law School Rankings | accessdate=2012-10-02 | archive-date=2016-10-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007044251/http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/cuny-03106 | dead-url=no }}</ref>创始之初该院附属于{{link-en|尼亚加拉大学|Niagara University}}，1891年被[[水牛城大学|水牛城大学]]吞并。<ref name="A HISTORY OF SUNY BUFFALO LAW SCHOOL">{{cite web | url=http://www.buffalo.edu/law125th.html | title=A HISTORY OF SUNY BUFFALO LAW SCHOOL | accessdate=2014-02-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209140838/http://www.buffalo.edu/law125th.html | archive-date=2014-02-09 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>该院是[[纽约州立大学|纽约州立大学]]中唯一的法学院。<ref name="SUNY Buffalo Law School ">{{cite web | url=http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/suny-buffalo-law-school-03113 | title=SUNY Buffalo Law School | accessdate=2014-02-16 | archive-date=2016-10-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024204904/http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/suny-buffalo-law-school-03113 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

